</listitem><listitem><para>If <emphasis>X</emphasis> is a list, all terms of the list are asserted or processed as directives</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>The term <emphasis>X</emphasis> is asserted instead of <emphasis><ref refid="classT" kindref="compound">T</ref></emphasis> </para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
